{"level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/b/ref=sd_allcat_ind_saf/191-0777068-9272724?ie=UTF8&node=318135011", "text": "Safety", "description_title": "Safety Supplies", "keyword_count": {"safety supplies": 3, "supplies": 4, "safety": 16}, "description_wc": 308, "description_text": "Safety supplies come in a variety of forms, including safety signs, personal protective equipment, and a wide array of other safety equipment. Safety supplies are used to mark an area, or to help protect persons from potentially hazardous conditions. Lock out tag out, sometimes referred to as lockout tagout (LO/TO), are safety procedures that use safety devices to help keep areas safe. Lock out tag out devices use color, warning labels or tags, and a physical barrier to temporarily prohibit machine operation or power activation, and reduce accidents, during maintenance or repair. Safety signs, or warning signs such as \u201cExit\u201d, \u201cDanger\u201d, or \u201cCaution\u201d, are used to display messaging and inform people of important circumstances. Personal protective equipment is anything from reflective chest coverings to hardhats, or Geiger counters & radiation detectors, used to detect the presence of ionizing radiation, to emergency response, first aid supplies, and eye wash units. Fire alarms and fire extinguishers are also used in safety. Additional safety products include: gloves, safety glasses, ear protection, hardhats, coveralls, fire-resistant clothing, rainwater & chemical splash apparel, and lab coats. Hazardous storage cabinets, and hazardous storage cans are safety equipment. Glove options include; cleanroom gloves, controlled environment gloves, cryogenic gloves, cut-resistant gloves, disposable gloves, and work gloves. Flags are a type of safety sign that come in a variety of colors, shapes, dimensions, and may have a magnetic, quick disconnect, or threaded hex base type. Flags can also come with reflective markings and lighting. Floor markers come in various types of adhesive tape, colors, markings (such as stripes, arrows, or words), and widths that can be used to mark an area. Safety mirrors are used as personal protective equipment. Safety supplies are used in construction sites, work sites, high-traffic areas, and in home applications. Safety equipment can meet various safety standards.", "parent_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "keyword_density": {"safety supplies": "2.0", "supplies": "1.3", "safety": "5.3"}}
{"level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Lab-Scientific-Supplies/b/ref=sd_allcat_ind_lab/191-0777068-9272724?ie=UTF8&node=317970011", "text": "Lab & Scientific", "description_title": "About Lab Equipment", "keyword_count": {"lab equipment": 4, "equipment": 7, "lab": 17}, "description_wc": 269, "description_text": "Lab Equipment includes a wide variety of laboratory supplies such as meters, microscopes, and purification systems that are used to facilitate scientific and educational processes. Researchers, educators, and hobbyists use lab equipment such as lab furnaces, microscopes, shakers, hot plates, and stirrers to assist in testing, measuring, inspecting, and data gathering. Microscopes, used to enhance the resolution of an object or image, are commonly used lab equipment, found in many biology, chemistry, and learning labs. Other laboratory equipment, such as furnaces, are used for heating applications that require a range of high temperatures. They heat to high temperatures evenly and maintain consistent temperatures, while providing an environment free of undesirable contaminants and moisture. Autoclaves are also commonly used laboratory supplies that assist in sterilization applications. Additional lab supplies include desiccators, which are seal-able enclosures used to protect contents from atmospheric moisture. A centrifuge is used to spin fluids of different densities to separate various parts, commonly blood and DNA samples. Laboratory equipment, such as lab baths and accessories, are used to assist with common lab operations. An electrophoresis apparatus is designed to run multiple groups of student samples at the same time. Lab supplies can be made from a wide variety of material types, selected for their application abilities such as temperature, water, or chemical resistance. Some lab supplies are designed to meet specific health, safety, and environmental standards. Lab equipment commonly operates with electrical or battery-powered sources, and may come with a warranty. Laboratory equipment is widely used in education, lab research, biology, metallurgy, engineering, chemistry, manufacturing, and in the medical, forensic science, and veterinary industries.", "parent_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "keyword_density": {"lab equipment": "3.0", "equipment": "2.6", "lab": "6.3"}}
{"level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/b/ref=sd_allcat_wt/191-0777068-9272724?ie=UTF8&node=15706571", "text": "Tires & Wheels", "description_title": "More about Tires, Rims, and Wheels", "keyword_count": {"tires": 11, "wheels": 4, "tires rims and wheels": 2, "tires rims": 3, "rims": 5}, "description_wc": 229, "description_text": "Amazon.com Automotive has a great selection of tires, rims, and wheels for your vehicle. Our wide selection of rims and tires allows any car enthusiast to quickly find and replace their current wheels, or improve their current vehicle. Our website allows customers to browse through a wide variety of tires, rims, or wheels based on need. For example, we have tires for trailers , commercial trucks , SUVs , RVs , and more. Our tire selection allows you to browse and find the correct products for whatever purpose. Our selection includes all-season tires , off-roading tires , performance tires , and more. We even have tires for motorcycles and ATVs . Our rims and tires don\u2019t come alone, either. Our pages have all the necessary tire accessories , wheel and rim accessories, and tire and wheel repair tools that you may need. This will allow you to purchase the necessary equipment to do tasks such as diagnose your wheel alignment and balancing. You can even find kits for rim and tire installation , so you can do it yourself and enhance your vehicle, whether it is a car, truck, or ATV, year round for every season. With Amazon.com\u2019s Part Finder tool you can find the perfect rim and tires that fit your vehicle. You can shop for tires, rims, and wheels confidently online at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "keyword_density": {"tires": "5.0", "wheels": "1.8", "tires rims and wheels": "3.7", "tires rims": "2.7", "rims": "2.3"}}
