{"level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/automotive-auto-truck-replacements-parts/b/ref=sd_allcat_apa/191-0777068-9272724?ie=UTF8&node=15684181", "text": "Automotive Parts & Accessories", "description_title": "More about Auto Parts and Accessories", "keyword_count": {"auto": 17, "parts and accessories": 3, "parts": 18, "auto parts": 12}, "description_wc": 252, "description_text": "The world of auto parts includes everything from performance parts to car care to tools and equipment for cars, trucks and even RVs. Amazon.com Automotive Parts and Accessories store presents this huge world of automotive products an organized online store with a number of refinements, so you can find the auto parts you need. For example, the Green Automotive section contains earth-friendly auto parts. Replacement Parts showcases auto parts to keep your car or truck in top shape. Interior auto parts , exterior auto parts and car care auto parts let you update and care for your ride. Our auto parts even include everything from wheel and tire care products to new rims and wheels. There are even gift ideas for the enthusiast. Amazon.com Automotive also has a helpful Part Finder tool that allows customers to find and filter products that fit their vehicle. You can browse through products with this tool, or even use it to filter down specific array of products. Browse the site and discover auto parts that make winter less stressful, parts and accessories for your RV, tools that help diagnose what\u2019s wrong, as well as parts to fix what ails your vehicle. You can even shop for auto parts by trusted name brands or find auto parts for specific vehicle brands like Chevrolet , Ford , or Ferrari . Even better, Amazon\u2019s Automotive Parts and Accessories store lets you shop for auto parts in one location from the comfort of your home or garage.", "parent_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "keyword_density": {"auto": "6.9", "parts and accessories": "3.6", "parts": "7.3", "auto parts": "9.7"}}
