{"nr_products": 13182630, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Sports-Collectibles/b/ref=sd_allcat_sprt_cllct/191-0777068-9272724?ie=UTF8&node=3250697011", "text": "Sports Collectibles", "description_title": "Sports Collectibles at Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {"sports collectibles": 8, "sports": 16}, "description_wc": 291, "description_text": "Welcome to our new Sports Collectibles store featuring sports memorabilia and sports collectibles from past, current and future stars from all major sport leagues and events including: Major League Baseball (MLB), National Football League (NFL), National Basketball Association (NBA), National Hockey League (NHL), Major League Soccer (MLS), NCAA, and Olympics. If you are looking to build your collection of sports collectibles and sports memorabilia or want to find a unique gift for an avid collector that will surprise them, our new store has the unique selection of sports memorabilia and sports collectibles that you are looking for. We focus on authentic sports collectibles and sports memorabilia, such as autographs and game-used jerseys authenticated by Ace Authentic, Frameworth, Highland Mint, Icon Sports Memorabilia, James Spence Authentication, MeiGray Group, MLB Players Alumni Association, Mounted Memories, NFL Players Inc., Panini Authentic, PSA/DNA, Steiner Sports, Topps, Tristar Authentic, and Upper Deck Authenticated. For the trading card collectors, we focus on having a large selection of wax packs and boxes, factory complete sets and single cards graded by Beckett Grading Services and Professional Sports Authenticator (PSA). As we continue to grow our selection, the Amazon Sports Collectibles Store is sure to have something for everybody. Whichever teams or players are your favorite, you should be able to find them amongst our giant selection of Authentic Game Used Merchandise, Autographed Jerseys, Balls, Bats, Shoes, Photos, Helmets, Trading cards, Other Sports Memorabilia and Sports Collectibles. Our new store will also have supplies such as display cases, ball cubes and card protectors, so whether you are adding to your collection, organizing your collection, or buying something as a gift, let the new Amazon Marketplace Sports Collectibles store help you find it.", "parent_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "keyword_density": {"sports collectibles": "5.6", "sports": "5.6"}}
