{"level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Desktops/b/ref=sd_allcat_deskserv/191-0777068-9272724?ie=UTF8&node=4972214011", "text": "Desktops & Monitors", "description_title": "Desktop Computers & Monitors at Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {"desktop computers": 4, "desktop": 5}, "description_wc": 268, "description_text": "Desktop computers are far from dead. Avid gamers, media professionals, or just home users looking for serious expandability all still look to desktop computers to suit their needs, and there are plenty of great machines available. Check out the best in desktop computers here at Amazon, from brands like Acer, Alienware, Apple, ASUS, CyberpowerPC, CybertronPC, Dell, Gateway, HP, iBUYPOWER, Lenovo, Sony, and Toshiba. You can check out our Desktop Buying Guide to find out a bit more about the right machine for you. Maybe you\u2019re looking for a newer all-in-one PC, where the monitor and CPU are a single unit, saving you all kinds of space in setting it up. Or maybe you\u2019re after the latest and greatest gaming PC--a good gaming PC is a cut above the average machine, with enhanced graphics, processing power, a supercharged cooling system, and other features to keep it at peak performance. Whether it\u2019s a gaming PC or any other type, you\u2019ll be covered here. Shop by price, brand, and other criteria such as desktop computers with a specific processor type (AMD or Intel). Check out best sellers, new releases, top rated and most gifted machines, and more. Once you\u2019ve picked out your machine you\u2019ll need to pick a monitor. Amazon has you covered there as well. Look for a monitor by size, check out monitor best sellers, choose between LCD and LED monitor types, and more. Whether you\u2019re after a massive high-definition monitor (for that gaming PC rig) or something a bit more modest, you\u2019ll find it here.", "parent_text": "Electronics & Computers", "keyword_density": {"desktop computers": "3.0", "desktop": "1.9"}}
{"level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Laptops-Tablets/b/ref=sd_allcat_lapnet/191-0777068-9272724?ie=UTF8&node=2956501011", "text": " Laptops, Ultrabooks & Tablets", "description_title": "Laptops, Ultrabooks & Tablets at Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {}, "description_wc": 328, "description_text": "Nowadays, it\u2019s all about portability. More and more of us have left behind the bulky desktop PC for these smaller, more mobile (and these days just as powerful) counterparts. Still haven\u2019t made the leap? Amazon is the perfect one-stop shop for a new laptop, tablet, or Ultrabook. With brands like Acer, Apple, ASUS, Dell, HP, Kindle Fire HD, Lenovo, Samsung, Sony, and Toshiba, you\u2019re sure to end up with a great machine. On the laptop front, you\u2019ll find all the standard styles, whether you\u2019re looking for a PC, Mac, Chromebook, Netbook, touchscreen laptop, Ultrabook, or more. Check out laptop best sellers, peruse our best deals, check out our helpful buying guides, and more\u2014you\u2019ll find just the right laptop model for you. If you\u2019re looking for a powerful, ultra-portable laptop, an Ultrabook may be just the right choice. An Ultrabook is a high-end subnotebook, outfitted with a low-power Intel processor, solid-state drive, and other technologies to give you a featherweight form-factor without losing performance or battery life. If you\u2019re unsure of which Ultrabook would suit your needs, our Ultrabook Buying Guide might be a good place to start. Or perhaps you\u2019re after a tablet? Tablet computing is increasingly popular, and it\u2019s no wonder why. These flat, touchscreen devices let you casually surf the web, enjoy music and video, play games, download and use apps (tablet speak for applications), read eBooks, and so much more. Our Tablet Buying Guide can help you find the right tablet for your needs, or you can check out best sellers, browse by brand, and more to do your research. You can also check out our selection of 2-in-1, aka convertible, machines, which combine a tablet and laptop in one. So whether you\u2019re looking for a laptop, Ultrabook, or tablet\u2014or even some combination of the above\u2014you\u2019ve come to the right place.", "parent_text": "Electronics & Computers", "keyword_density": {}}
